List of the page layout part parameters
---------------------------------------

Here is the list of the parameters you can use in the pages :
{%- for param in params %}
- {{param['name']}}_off
{%- endfor %}

With one of the parameters, you can deactivate some part of the page template.
To activate a parameter, you need to define the variable. The command for each parameter is the following :

{%- for param in params %}
    <!-- var(page:{{param['name']}}_off)="off" -->
{%- endfor %}

If you define one variable, the html part will be removed.
The test to disable the part is the following : 

    if NAME_off is undefined


